    "As can be seen in Fig. 3, each plotted value of the MAE represents the minimum achieved value at specific K (i.e.",
    "nearest neighbors of items) for each distinct value of parameter α.",
    "To sum up, the minimum value of MAE is (0.766433) and is achieved when parameter is 0.6 and the size of the K parameter is 60.",
    "Note that the obtained results for using different values of K are not reported here due to space availability.As shown in Fig. 3, note that when = 0, the prediction accuracy of the proposed recommendation approach is weak as the MAE value is quite high.",
    "In this case, the semantic similarity is not taken into account to generate recommendations and only the Item-based CF approach is considered (see Formula 9)."
